-- Saudi Grand Mufti Condemns Protests as Dangerous, Al-Watan Says
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-11-28T15:51:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-28/saudi-grand-mufti-condemns-protests-as-dangerous-al-watan-says.html
 The top cleric in  Saudi Arabia ,
home to Islam’s holiest cities, has criticized protests in the
Middle East as being un-Islamic,  al-Watan  newspaper reported.  Demonstrations are a “bad and dangerous thing” that
threat unity in the Islamic world, Grand Mufti Sheikh Abdulaziz
bin Abdullah al-Sheikh was cited as saying by al-Watan today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  